import {
  GridItem,
  Text,
  Center,
  Stack,
  Heading,
  Image,
  Box,
} from '@chakra-ui/layout'
import React from 'react'

const AspectJesse = () => {
  return (
    <GridItem colStart={1} colSpan={4}>
      <Stack p={3} rounded={'md'} bg={'blackAlpha.400'}>
        <Center w={'100%'}>
          <Heading as={'h3'} size={'lg'} fontSize={'3xl'}>
            Religion and Ritual Life

        <Box>
          <Text>Hello World</Text>
        </Box>
      </Stack>
    </GridItem>
  )
}

export default AspectJesse
